name: Altcoinist Token
description: Altcoinist is an autonomous onchain trading ecosystem on Base, building towards the future where anyone can say “make me money” and let AI agents & trading tools handle the rest. By combining automation, AI-driven execution, and decentralized financial tools, Altcoinist aims to deliver mass-adoption-ready, fully autonomous trenching (onchain trading). The ecosystem’s flagship product, the Altcoinist Trench Bot, is a Telegram-based trading bot that fuses artificial and human intelligence for automated early trade entries, personalized, autonomous trade strategies with institutional-grade data and trade execution.
